headline: State Street to Speak at the Goldman Sachs 2024 U.S. Financial Services Conference
summary: BOSTON, November 29, 2024--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) announced today that its Chairman & Chief Executive Officer, Ron O’Hanley, and its Vice Chairman & Chief Financial Officer, Eric Aboaf, will present at the Goldman Sachs U.S. Financial Services Conference in New York, NY on Tuesday, December 10, 2024 at approximately 3:40 pm ET.
